get.description:
Stream real-time download progress via Server-Sent Events (SSE).

Frontend usage:
    const eventSource = new EventSource('/downloader/progress/{task_id}/stream');
    eventSource.onmessage = (event) => {
        const data = JSON.parse(event.data);
        console.log('Progress:', data.progress + '%');
    };

Args:
    task_id (str): Task ID returned from /download endpoint

Returns:
    EventSourceResponse: SSE stream of progress updates
